room_title: Escape room "New Blood, New World" by Crack It! Escape Game in Jacksonville (NC)
room_description: Legend is told of a mysterious ship that appears off the coast of North Carolina every year at this time. Your team of supernatural investigators must board the ship and recover an ancient family heirloom to return it to the last living relative of Professor Lionheart. Lionheart, was last heard from in 1973 and his family has lost all hope of learning his fate. Choose your team of adventurers and board the vessel to determine what happened to Lionheart and return the heirloom to his family.
